contents.name: Smile for Me
contents.resume: The bouquet including Alstroemeria and Tied with satin ribbon
contents.description: The bouquet can be prepared for delivery in 20 minutes, including: Alstroemeria ligh- pink, Alstroemeria yellow, Tied with satin ribbon - 3 pieces. Infuse happiness into your friendship and bring friends closer with this beautiful bunch.A luxurious medley of pretty pink and yellow alstromerias with a mass of green foliage will be a nice surprise for any occasion.
